| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5280 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6326eadc-efec-5afc-9549-cf4b018eb8e1"
